Local Vegan Bakery Delivery

30 years of baking vegan deserts, offering delivery and catering in Colorado.

Get in touch

Services

What We Do

We only use organic and vegan baking ingredient that are fresh and local as possible.

We have different sizes of boxes available for various appetites, from individuals to families.

We offer a flexible catering service to your special events as well as table presentations.

Our Vegan Bakery in Numbers

157

households per month

10

experts working

5

awards won

100%

satisfied customers

Why You'll Love Us

There is never been a better time to eat organic. Organic means working with nature.

  • Delicious
  • Ethical
  • Sustainable
  • Seasonal
  • Free delivery

"Excellent Service"

Their service is brilliant! I told all my friends about their homemade sourdough bread!

Fiona

We were very happy that they were able to delivery to our wedding!
